<plot>"Morni Ki Raag" is an exploration of the struggle undergone by young servants in India who are deprived of their childhood and all the potential that goes hand in hand with that early age. The film deals specifically with questions of literacy as a young maid finds herself ensnared within societal and familial tensions, all the while attempting to reconcile her reality with her dreams of learning to read.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?377520</url></doc>
